{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "name": "Calendar",
  "slug": "soc-calendar",
  "description": "Daily ticket volume with label breakdown and annotations.",
  "tags": [
    "socmetric"
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "099fb995346f31c7",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "body": "**SOCMetric** \u00b7 Last sync: `<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.last_sync_completed_at | relative_time>>` \u00b7 Status: `<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.last_sync_status>>`"
    },
    {
      "id": "d72e5ee9b3678339",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "body": "| [Home](/pages/soc-dashboard-home) | [Calendar](/pages/soc-calendar) | [Watch Status](/pages/soc-watch-status) | [Flow](/pages/soc-flow) | [Response Speed](/pages/soc-response-speed) | [Capacity](/pages/soc-capacity) | [Patterns](/pages/soc-patterns) | [Projections](/pages/soc-projections) | [Context Ledger](/pages/soc-context-ledger) | [Setup](/pages/soc-setup) |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "63d721d24d2dde77",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "visibility_formula": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.first_sync_completed_at == null>>",
      "body": "> Setup is incomplete. Open the [Setup page](/pages/soc-setup) to configure the project, classify statuses, and run the first sync."
    },
    {
      "id": "436c3ea4ea5ce7a6",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "### Month: `<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.calendar_view_month | default(NOW() | date_format('yyyy-MM'))>>`"
    },
    {
      "id": "fcb08b164ac83e09",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "< Prev month",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "settings_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "calendar_view_month",
          "value": "<<DATE_FORMAT(DATE_SUBTRACT(DATE_PARSE(RESOURCE.soc_settings.calendar_view_month + '-01'), 1, 'months'), 'yyyy-MM')>>"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d0cab90d8d20d57e",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Next month >",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "settings_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "calendar_view_month",
          "value": "<<DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(DATE_PARSE(RESOURCE.soc_settings.calendar_view_month + '-01'), 1, 'months'), 'yyyy-MM')>>"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ff4a008470319a22",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "<div class='cal-grid'>\n<<FOR d IN CALENDAR_CELLS(RESOURCE.soc_settings.calendar_view_month)>>\n  <div class='cell <<d.is_current_month ? '' : 'dim'>> <<IS_TODAY(d.date) ? 'today' : ''>>'>\n    <div class='day-num'><<d.day>></div>\n    <div class='total'><<RESOURCE.soc_metrics_cache.calendar.days | find(date == d.date) | pluck('total') | default(0)>></div>\n    <div class='labels'>\n      <<FOR l IN (RESOURCE.soc_metrics_cache.calendar.days | find(date == d.date) | pluck('labels') | default([]))>>\n        <span class='chip' style='background: <<HASH_COLOR(l.label)>>'><<l.label>>: <<l.count>></span>\n      <<ENDFOR>>\n    </div>\n    <div class='note'><<RESOURCE.soc_day_annotations[d.date]>></div>\n  </div>\n<<ENDFOR>>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "53325e93c4f14ba0",
      "type": "form",
      "title": "Annotate a day",
      "fields": [
        {
          "key": "date",
          "type": "date",
          "label": "Date"
        },
        {
          "key": "annotation",
          "type": "text",
          "label": "Note"
        }
      ],
      "submit": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "annotations_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "<<fields.date>>",
          "value": "<<fields.annotation>>"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "access": "tenant",
  "exported_at": "2026-04-21T00:00:00Z"
}